{"text_id":144188,"tokens":["#"," How"," to"," Do"," Sto","ichio","metry","\n\n","Sto","ichio","metry"," is"," the"," calculation"," of"," reactants"," and"," products"," in"," chemical"," reactions","."," This"," method"," plays"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," understanding"," how"," to"," predict"," the"," quantities"," needed"," or"," produced"," in"," a"," reaction","."," Follow"," these"," steps"," to"," conduct"," comprehensive"," stoichio","metric"," calculations",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","1",":"," Write"," Down"," the"," Number"," of"," Atoms","\n","Start"," by"," writing"," down"," the"," number"," of"," atoms"," that"," comprise"," each"," compound"," on"," either"," side"," of"," the"," equation","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," keep"," track"," of"," the"," atoms"," involved"," in"," the"," reaction"," and"," ensure"," both"," sides"," of"," the"," equation"," are"," balanced",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","2",":"," Add"," a"," Coefficient"," in"," Front"," of"," Elements","\n","Add"," a"," coefficient"," (","a"," whole"," number",")"," in"," front"," of"," elements"," that"," are"," not"," oxygen"," and"," hydrogen"," to"," balance"," each"," side"," of"," the"," equation","."," These"," coefficients"," represent"," the"," number"," of"," molecules"," or"," moles"," of"," a"," substance",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","3",":"," Balance"," the"," Hydrogen"," and"," Oxygen"," Atoms","\n","Once"," you"," have"," balanced"," the"," other"," elements",","," focus"," on"," hydrogen"," and"," oxygen"," atoms","."," These"," are"," usually"," balanced"," last"," because"," they"," are"," often"," found"," in"," multiple"," compounds"," within"," a"," reaction",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","4",":"," Re","-","count"," the"," Number"," of"," Atoms","\n","Re","-","count"," the"," number"," of"," atoms"," on"," each"," side"," of"," the"," equation","."," Make"," sure"," they"," are"," equal","."," If"," not",","," adjust"," the"," coefficients"," accordingly"," until"," both"," sides"," are"," balanced",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","5",":"," Calculate"," the"," M","olar"," Mass","\n","Identify"," the"," compound"," given"," in"," grams"," and"," calculate"," its"," molar"," mass","."," M","olar"," mass"," is"," the"," mass"," of"," one"," mole"," of"," a"," substance"," and"," can"," be"," found"," using"," the"," periodic"," table",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","6",":"," Convert"," Grams"," to"," Moles","\n","Convert"," the"," given"," grams"," of"," the"," substance"," to"," moles"," by"," dividing"," the"," mass"," of"," the"," compound"," by"," its"," molar"," mass","."," This"," conversion"," is"," crucial"," for"," comparing"," substances"," in"," a"," reaction",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","7",":"," Determine"," the"," M","olar"," Ratio","\n","Determine"," the"," molar"," ratio"," between"," reactants"," by"," looking"," at"," the"," coefficients"," in"," the"," balanced"," equation","."," This"," ratio"," will"," guide"," you"," in"," conversion"," between"," different"," reactants"," or"," products",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","8",":"," Cross","-","Multiply"," by"," the"," M","olar"," Ratio","\n","Cross","-","multiply"," by"," the"," molar"," ratio"," to"," find"," moles"," of"," another"," reactant"," or"," product","."," This"," step"," involves"," simple"," multiplication"," and"," division"," using"," the"," molar"," ratios"," from"," the"," balanced"," equation",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","9",":"," Convert"," Moles"," Back"," to"," Mass","\n","Convert"," moles"," back"," to"," mass"," by"," using"," the"," molar"," mass"," of"," the"," species"," involved","."," Multiply"," the"," number"," of"," moles"," by"," the"," molar"," mass"," to"," find"," the"," mass"," in"," grams",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","1","0",":"," Determine"," if"," the"," Reaction"," is"," at"," STP","\n","Assess"," if"," the"," reaction"," is"," happening"," at"," standard"," temperature"," and"," pressure"," (","STP",")."," STP"," conditions"," (","0","\u00b0","C"," and"," ","1"," atm"," pressure",")"," simplify"," gas"," calculations",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","1","1",":"," Use"," the"," Conversion"," Factor"," ","2","2",".","4","1","4"," L","/","mol","\n","If"," the"," reaction"," is"," at"," STP",","," use"," the"," conversion"," factor"," ","2","2",".","4","1","4"," liters"," per"," mole"," to"," convert"," liters"," of"," gas"," to"," moles","."," This"," is"," a"," standard"," value"," used"," under"," STP"," conditions",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","1","2",":"," Use"," the"," Ideal"," Gas"," Law","\n","If"," the"," reaction"," is"," not"," at"," STP",","," use"," the"," ideal"," gas"," law"," (","PV"," ="," n","RT",")"," to"," convert"," liters"," of"," gas"," to"," moles","."," Here",","," P"," is"," pressure",","," V"," is"," volume",","," n"," is"," number"," of"," moles",","," R"," is"," the"," ideal"," gas"," constant",","," and"," T"," is"," temperature"," in"," Kelvin",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","1","3",":"," Calculate"," the"," Density"," of"," the"," Liquid","\n","For"," liquid"," reactants"," or"," products",","," calculate"," the"," density","."," Density"," is"," the"," mass"," per"," unit"," volume"," and"," can"," be"," used"," for"," conversion"," purposes",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","1","4",":"," Convert"," Volume"," to"," mL","\n","Convert"," the"," volume"," of"," the"," liquid"," to"," milli","liters"," (","mL",")."," Volume"," conversions"," ensure"," the"," correct"," application"," of"," density"," in"," calculations",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","1","5",":"," Multiply"," Volume"," by"," Density","\n","Multiply"," the"," volume"," in"," milli","liters"," by"," the"," density"," to"," find"," the"," mass"," of"," the"," liquid"," reactant"," or"," product","."," This"," step"," helps"," you"," to"," move"," between"," volumes"," and"," masses"," for"," liquid"," substances",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","1","6",":"," Calculate"," the"," M","olar"," Mass"," of"," the"," React","ant","\n","Re","visit"," the"," initial"," step"," of"," calculating"," the"," molar"," mass",","," especially"," if"," you"," are"," dealing"," with"," a"," different"," reactant"," or"," product"," later"," in"," the"," reaction",".","\n\n","###"," Step"," ","1","7",":"," Convert"," Grams"," of"," a"," Substance"," to"," Moles","\n","Finally",","," again"," convert"," grams"," of"," any"," new"," substance"," to"," moles"," using"," its"," molar"," mass","."," This"," reiter","ative"," conversion"," may"," be"," necessary"," when"," you"," deal"," with"," multiple"," substances"," in"," a"," complex"," reaction",".","\n\n","By"," following"," these"," detailed"," steps",","," performing"," stoichio","metric"," calculations"," becomes"," systematic"," and"," accurate","."," With"," practice",","," stoichio","metry"," will"," become"," a"," valuable"," skill"," in"," predicting"," and"," understanding"," chemical"," reactions","."],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"gpt4o","label":1}